This is the constructor method of Taxer It initializes lists of taxis, drivers, taxis with drivers, and the taxis available the list taxis contains the taxis from our database the list drivers contains drivers from our database the list taxisWithDriver will contain the taxis with a driver given the list taxisAvailable will contain the taxis with driver available for a ride
